column5: I will be going up to that area this weekend as well.  I booked it about 6 months ago with a bunch of guys from church.  We are staying at the West Arm Lodge.  Don't know if that is far from you guys but if it isn't, maybe I will see a few of you out there.  Have a great weekend.
....I'll be fishing over that way from time to time. Are you in a rental or your own boat?
probably a rental. I don't have a vehicle to pull my boat at the moment.  My boat is a bit small as well. Is Lakair far from West Arm Lodge.
....Not certain on the distance, exactly. I'd say 3, maybe 4 miles. Lakair would be on your left side just before you pass under the Hwy #64 bridge.
